                            <comment id="13904070" author="cheolsoo" created="Tue, 18 Feb 2014 14:08:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;PigStats is not initialized means PigServer hasn&apos;t started yet. So setError[Messages|Code|Throwable]() can simply exit in that case.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attached is a patch that adds null checks to setError[Messages|Code|Throwable]().&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
